s. A modified version made NanoCas even more effective by improving how wel=
l it binds to DNA. NanoCas&#8217; small size and strong performance could u=
nlock potential gene editing treatments for muscle, the heart, and the brai=
n. </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/fc977f2a-b96f-4016-a71f-=
